{"word":"G1684 - ἐμβαίνω - embaínō - em-ba'-hee-no - Come into","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐμβαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">embaínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">em-ba'-hee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come into</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஏறு, இறங்கு"},{"paragraph":"to go into, step into"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a>; to <i>walk on</i>, that is, <i>embark</i> (aboard a vessel), <i>reach</i> (a pool): - come (get) into, enter (into), go (up) into, step in, take ship.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}